var e=[{id:`L2_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`오랜 고민 끝에, 당신은 한 가지 중요한 사실을 깨달았다.`,JPN:`長い間悩んだ結果、あなたは一つ大事なことに気づいた。`,ENG:`After much debate, you came to the conclusion`,TWN:`苦惱許久後，你意識到一個重要的事實。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_SILENCE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L3_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`줄곧 생각해 온 그녀야말로, 앞으로 마주할 운명에서 꼭 필요한 존재라는 것을.`,JPN:`ずっと考えてきた彼女だからこそ、これから向き合う運命に必ず必要な存在であることを。`,ENG:`that this employee, whom you'd been giving a lot of thought to, was absolutely necessary for the future ahead.`,TWN:`一直盤踞在腦海中的她，是你在未來必須要面對的命運中，一個不可或缺的存在。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_SILENCE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L4_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`그리하여 당신은 결심했다.`,JPN:`そして、あなたは決心した。`,ENG:`So, you've decided`,TWN:`所以你決定了。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_SILENCE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L5_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`이 세계에서 어떤 결말을 마주하더라도, 마지막까지 그녀와 함께하기로.`,JPN:`この世界でどのような結末を迎えるとしても、最後まで彼女とともにいることを。`,ENG:`that you'll be with her, no matter the consequences.`,TWN:`不管這個世界會迎來怎樣的結局，你都要和她一起走到最後。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_SILENCE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L6_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`마음의 준비를 마치고 사장실로 호출하자, 곧 도착한다는 응답이 돌아왔다.`,JPN:`意を決して社長室へ呼び出すと、もうすぐ着くとの応答が返ってきた。`,ENG:`Having decided that, you called her to your office. She said she'd be here soon.`,TWN:`下定決心後，你呼叫她到老闆辦公室，得到回應說她馬上就到。`},stage:{bg:`BLACK`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_SILENCE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:null,R:null}}},{id:`L12_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`이런 말하면 어떻게 들릴 지 모르겠지만, 난 세상을 지키기 위해 태어났어.`,JPN:`こういうことを話すとどう聞こえるかわからないけど、私は世界を守るために生まれたの。`,ENG:`I don't know how this'll sound, but I was born to protect the world.`,TWN:`I don't know how this'll sound, but I was born to protect the world.`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,face:`UNIT_SERIOUS`},R:null}}},{id:`L13_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`그게 내가 존재하는 이유이고, 내가 맡은 역할이야.`,JPN:`それが私の存在理由で、私の役割よ。`,ENG:`That's the sole purpose of my existence.`,TWN:`That's the sole purpose of my existence.`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L14_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`언제까지 이 세계에 있을지는 모르겠지만. 당신이 하는 일도 모두 당신의 세계를 지키기 위한 거잖아?`,JPN:`この世界にこれからどのくらい留まることになるかわからないけど、貴方のやってることも全部、結局貴方の世界を守りたいのでしょ？`,ENG:`I don't know how long I'll be here, but everything you do is to protect your world, right?`,TWN:`I don't know how long I'll be here, but everything you do is to protect your world, right?`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L15_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`그러니까 내가 힘이 돼줄게. 당신이 나를 도와주고 싶어 하는 것처럼 말야.`,JPN:`だから私が力になってあげる。貴方が私の力になりたいと思っているように。`,ENG:`So, I'll help you. Like how you're trying to help me.`,TWN:`So, I'll help you. Like how you're trying to help me.`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,face:`UNIT_PRIDE`},R:null}}},{id:`L16_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`자! 그럼 헹가래 치면서 마무리하자! 무서워하지 말고 이리 와～`,JPN:`さて！　それでは胴上げをして終わりにしようか？　怖がらないでこっちに来て～`,ENG:`All right! Now, let me toss you up and down and we'll call it a day. C'mon, don't be scared! Come closer!`,TWN:`All right! Now, let me toss you up and down and we'll call it a day. C'mon, don't be scared! Come closer!`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`JACKO_GUILTY_CA_NULL`,face:`UNIT_LAUGH`},R:null}}}];export{e as default};